materials_text: {"blocks":[{"key":"ecfd9","text":"Reagents :","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":0,"length":10},{"style":"UNDERLINE","offset":0,"length":10}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"2lcb9","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"87vva","text":"- TBS 10X : Tris base 121.1g + NaCl 90g in 1L H2O.pH 7.4.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"db5kk","text":"- TBS 1X-Triton 0,5%","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"89tdt","text":"- Xilen","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"38i1e","text":"- Ethanol : 100%, 95%, 70%","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"9ena6","text":"- Unmasking buffer epitopes : Citrate solution 10mM pH6.0","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"372lp","text":"- Blocking Buffer : TBS 1X + 5% NGS","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"3eehl","text":"- 1st Ab : Diluted in1X PBS +2%NGS","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"c04","text":"- 2nd Ab : Diluted in1X PBS +2%NGS","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"60aqi","text":"- Endogenous peroxidase blocking solution : TBS 1x + 3% H2O2(30%) + 10% methanol","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

status.info: We use this protocol and it's working

steps.step: {"blocks":[{"key":"bb3pp","text":"Put the slides 30 min in the incubator at 60ºC.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"ftoa3","text":"Put the slides 10 min in endogenous peroxidase blocking solution: TBS 1x + 3% H2O2 + 10% methanol","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
{"blocks":[{"key":"36api","text":"Put sections in 200 mL of citrate buffer 10mM, pH 6","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
{"blocks":[{"key":"dq000","text":"Put sections in a boiling water bath for 20 min","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
{"blocks":[{"key":"8ljbc","text":"Let sections cool down for 20 min at RT","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
{"blocks":[{"key":"4ks4a","text":"Put wet paper in a black box for immunohistochemistry","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"9f6gn","text":"Gently dry and circle sections with the hydrophobic pen ImmEdge Vector H 4000 without touching the tissue ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"9fora","text":"Put 200ul/slide of TBS 1X + 2% NGS + primary Ab48/72h (it depends of the Ab) at 4ºC (cold room)","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"42cfp","text":"At this step it is important to prepare ABC solution and let it, at least, 30 min on the shaker","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"3g3q3","text":"Incubate 1 hour at RT with ABC solution (4drops A/B in 10 mL of TBS 1x)","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"6f8io","text":"In aluminium foil: DAB Standard Kit: 1 drop of reagent B in 1 mL of reagent A (gives rise to brown staining)","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"219cv","text":"In aluminium foil: Vector SG: 3 drops Chromogen + 3 drops Hydrogen Peroxide in 5mL PBS (gives rise to blue staining)","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"5gb69","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"79v14","text":"Put 200 uL on each section and put a cardboard box on it to keep darkness for a time ranging from 3-15 minutes depending on the antibody used","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"8an0v","text":"Remove with an air-pump equipment and clean the material with bleach","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"ficnc","text":"Puta line of mounting medium(DPX) byslide.Put the coverslip (washed with ethanol previously) on the slide. Remove bubbles","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
{"blocks":[{"key":"4rj22","text":"Let dry the slides on the tray in the hood overnight","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
